ngram\": \"a prohibited drug\", \"from\": 607, \"to\": 624}, {\"ngram\": \"a criminal group\", \"from\": 646, \"to\": 662}, {\"ngram\": \"November\", \"from\": 685, \"to\": 693}, {\"ngram\": \"five years and six months' imprisonment\", \"from\": 702, \"to\": 741}, {\"ngram\": \"his arrest\", \"from\": 756, \"to\": 766}, {\"ngram\": \"February\", \"from\": 770, \"to\": 778}]}, {\"sentence\": \"His three-year non-parole period expired in February for those charges, but he was subsequently charged with further offences which had not yet been finalised, preventing his release.\", \"from\": 786, \"to\": 969, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"His three-year non-parole period\", \"from\": 786, \"to\": 818}, {\"ngram\": \"February\", \"from\": 830, \"to\": 838}, {\"ngram\": \"those charges\", \"from\": 843, \"to\": 856}, {\"ngram\": \"further offences\", \"from\": 895, \"to\": 911}, {\"ngram\": \"his release\", \"from\": 957, \"to\": 968}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The NSW District Court in May convicted Miller after he pleaded guilty to supplying more than 500 grams of methamphetamine, while another charge of participating in a criminal group was taken into account in his sentencing.\", \"from\": 971, \"to\": 1194, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 975, \"end\": 993, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/District_Court_of_New_South_Wales\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"NSW District Court\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/District_Court_of_New_South_Wales\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/District_Court_of_New_South_Wales\"}, {\"begin\": 975, \"end\": 993, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/District_Court_of_New_South_Wales\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"NSW District Court\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/District_Court_of_New_South_Wales\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/District_Court_of_New_South_Wales\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"May\", \"from\": 997, \"to\": 1000}, {\"ngram\": \"Miller\", \"from\": 1011, \"to\": 1017}, {\"ngram\": \"more than 500 grams\", \"from\": 1055, \"to\": 1074}, {\"ngram\": \"methamphetamine\", \"from\": 1078, \"to\": 1093}, {\"ngram\": \"another charge\", \"from\": 1101, \"to\": 1115}, {\"ngram\": \"a criminal group\", \"from\": 1136, \"to\": 1152}, {\"ngram\": \"account\", \"from\": 1168, \"to\": 1175}, {\"ngram\": \"his sentencing\", \"from\": 1179, \"to\": 1193}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Judge Andrew Scotting found special circumstances as the charges would have attracted partial accumulation in his sentence if they had been dealt with alongside the earlier offences.\", \"from\": 1196, \"to\": 1378, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Judge Andrew Scotting\", \"from\": 1196, \"to\": 1217}, {\"ngram\": \"special circumstances\", \"from\": 1224, \"to\": 1245}, {\"ngram\": \"the charges\", \"from\": 1249, \"to\": 1260}, {\"ngram\": \"partial accumulation\", \"from\": 1282, \"to\": 1302}, {\"ngram\": \"his sentence\", \"from\": 1306, \"to\": 1318}, {\"ngram\": \"the earlier offences\", \"from\": 1357, \"to\": 1377}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"This is an unusual case,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 1380, \"to\": 1415, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an unusual case\", \"from\": 1389, \"to\": 1404}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It is rare for the court to be able to assess an offender at the end of their non-parole period ... the point has been reached where no further rehabilitative benefit will be obtained by keeping the offender in custody,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 1417, \"to\": 1647, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the court\", \"from\": 1433, \"to\": 1442}, {\"ngram\": \"an offender\", \"from\": 1464, \"to\": 1475}, {\"ngram\": \"the end\", \"from\": 1479, \"to\": 1486}, {\"ngram\": \"their non-parole period\", \"from\": 1490, \"to\": 1513}, {\"ngram\": \"the point\", \"from\": 1518, \"to\": 1527}, {\"ngram\": \"no further rehabilitative benefit\", \"from\": 1551, \"to\": 1584}, {\"ngram\": \"the offender\", \"from\": 1613, \"to\": 1625}, {\"ngram\": \"custody\", \"from\": 1629, \"to\": 1636}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He sentenced Miller to four years and three months with a non-parole period of one year, again backdated, and expiring less than a week later on May 15.\", \"from\": 1649, \"to\": 1801, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Miller\", \"from\": 1662, \"to\": 1668}, {\"ngram\": \"four years\", \"from\": 1672, \"to\": 1682}, {\"ngram\": \"three months\", \"from\": 1687, \"to\": 1699}, {\"ngram\": \"a non-parole period\", \"from\": 1705, \"to\": 1724}, {\"ngram\": \"one year\", \"from\": 1728, \"to\": 1736}, {\"ngram\": \"May\", \"from\": 1794, \"to\": 1797}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It allowed Miller to apply for parole again, under the provision of manifest injustice, meaning he could avoid a 12-month waiting period.\", \"from\": 1803, \"to\": 1940, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Miller\", \"from\": 1814, \"to\": 1820}, {\"ngram\": \"parole\", \"from\": 1834, \"to\": 1840}, {\"ngram\": \"the provision\", \"from\": 1854, \"to\": 1867}, {\"ngram\": \"manifest injustice\", \"from\": 1871, \"to\": 1889}, {\"ngram\": \"a 12-month waiting period\", \"from\": 1914, \"to\": 1939}]}, {\"sentence\": \"His release was granted following Community Corrections assessing Miller as having a low-medium risk of reoffending, recommending his release to supervised parole.\", \"from\": 1942, \"to\": 2105, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"His release\", \"from\": 1942, \"to\": 1953}, {\"ngram\": \"Community Corrections\", \"from\": 1976, \"to\": 1997}, {\"ngram\": \"Miller\", \"from\": 2008, \"to\": 2014}, {\"ngram\": \"a low-medium risk\", \"from\": 2025, \"to\": 2042}, {\"ngram\": \"his release\", \"from\": 2072, \"to\": 2083}, {\"ngram\": \"supervised parole\", \"from\": 2087, \"to\": 2104}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He had displayed some insight into his long history of substance abu