 in a medley relay.\", \"from\": 2575, \"to\": 2695, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2620, \"end\": 2641, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1996_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 5.879862022917472e-13, \"text\": \"1996 Atlanta Olympics\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1996_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1996_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 2625, \"end\": 2641, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1996_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.6750021599725644e-14, \"text\": \"Atlanta Olympics\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1996_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1996_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The former swimmer\", \"from\": 2575, \"to\": 2593}, {\"ngram\": \"a silver medal\", \"from\": 2598, \"to\": 2612}, {\"ngram\": \"the butterfly event\", \"from\": 2645, \"to\": 2664}, {\"ngram\": \"bronze\", \"from\": 2670, \"to\": 2676}, {\"ngram\": \"a medley relay\", \"from\": 2680, \"to\": 2694}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The court was told he was devastated not to win gold and struggled to adjust to life after competitive sport.\", \"from\": 2697, \"to\": 2806, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The court\", \"from\": 2697, \"to\": 2706}, {\"ngram\": \"gold\", \"from\": 2745, \"to\": 2749}, {\"ngram\": \"life\", \"from\": 2777, \"to\": 2781}, {\"ngram\": \"competitive sport\", \"from\": 2788, \"to\": 2805}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He was not selected for the 2000 Sydney Olympics, after injuries and an introduction to drugs through the fashion and media industry contacts of his first wife during their brief marriage, Miller told the court.\", \"from\": 2808, \"to\": 3019, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2836, \"end\": 2856, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2000_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999999993551683, \"rank\": 6.446192988630052e-10, \"text\": \"2000 Sydney Oly